Global Organic Dairy Products Market Insights
Organic Dairy Products Market size was valued at USD 22.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 38.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.


Organic Dairy Products Market Overview
The organic dairy products market is expected to experience robust growth, with a projected market size of USD 25.2 billion in 2025. This growth can be attributed to an increasing consumer preference for natural and chemical-free food items. Organic dairy products are gaining popularity due to rising health awareness, higher disposable incomes, and a shift toward cleaner diets. The market is driven by the expanding organic food sector and increasing demand from regions such as North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific. The projected CAGR (Compound Annual Growth Rate) for the organic dairy products market is estimated to be 6.5% between 2025-2030.

